GG version of my map named "Rust n' Dust". ----
Started out as just messing around with the clip tool but turned into something interesting, turned out to be my most visually pleasing map. Probably not to great to play on though, it was pretty fun with bots but when there's real players you'll probably get shot before you can get to any of the interesting areas, but it might work out, I can't say for sure as I haven't played it with real people. Here's a video of the map I took in Gmod, Also available on YouTube but it's much lower quality there, http://youtube.com/watch?v=BkbWk9O9I_w.
